reviewText: I like much watching my gullah video with my newborn baby he can not get enough!!!!!!!! Because we like sometimes i watch Gullah Gullah island while im awake and asleep but not when im too tired! For my 34th birthday i hope to get this tape because gullah gullah BINYA BINYA POLYWAG!!!! If i don't watch gullah gullah i get very cranky and sleepy... so hurry up and watch it !!!!!! :-)
My son borrowed this video from the libray. He loved the music and Binyah Binyah so much that he asked for the video from Santa. He is 3 years old and it is a great video for children, ages 1-4
